	<h2 class="entry-title">
		<a href="index.html?p=149" title="Permalink to A Brief Reprieve" rel="bookmark">A Brief Reprieve</a>
	</h2>
	<div class="meta">
		<p>Published June 10, 2008 by Rob Glazebrook.</p>
	</div>	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Dear Constant Reader,</p>
<p>I apologize for the lack of new articles so far this week. It seems I have what doctors are calling &#8220;Strep Throat,&#8221; and that&#8217;s taking a lot out of me physically and, due to the fever I&#8217;m guessing, also mentally. I&#8217;m hoping to get back to a regular writing schedule by the end of this week.</p>
<p>In the meantime, I thought I would share a bit of good news. As of late last week, CSSnewbie has over 1,000 RSS feed subscribers! I truly and deeply appreciate all of you who have taken the time to subscribe to my feed and come back week after week. Without you, I&#8217;d be just another crazy in the park, shouting at the pigeons about web development. And the world does not need another one of those crazies.</p>
<!-- Quick Adsense WordPress Plugin: http://quicksense.net/ -->
